name: Uv5r
body:
UV-5R is a software programming solution for the [Baofeng UV5R](http://uv5r.net) radio. 
The UV-5R is a VHFand UHF Handheld radio.
136-174 MHz - 400-480 MHz
4 Watts/1 Watt Transmit Power
